  "description": "<i>Lakers vs. Celtics</i> on Genesis is an update of the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/dos/lakers-versus-celtics-and-the-nba-playoffs\">game of the same name for PCs</a>. It features the same perspective, same action-oriented gameplay with an emphasis on offense, and the same game modes: exhibition games and the playoff tournament mode. <br><br>It features ten NBA teams from the '89-'90 season. Compared to the PC version, it also adds more signature moves, different home- and away-jerseys, animated coaches, TV-style scenes from other games in the halftime show, player portraits for the starting five, voice samples for the referee and counts the number of personal fouls a players has committed, making it possible for them to foul out.",
